Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.76,0:00:09.84,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:20.37,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:39.35,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:46.81,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:53.90,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.56,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:07.04,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:14.31,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.31,0:01:21.05,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.05,0:01:28.48,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:01:59.76,Titles,,90,0,0,,The Door to a New World
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:25.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've never seen\Nsuch insubordination!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:28.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is why I was against\Ndisbanding Rubor and Caput!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:35.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,We cannot afford to rely\Nsolely on Chor Tempest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:36.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Gather all our troops and Similes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:39.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,The patrol Similes and the\Ncruise Similes. I want them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:40.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:42.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,What a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:47.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Conflict will not\Nbring about a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:04.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:27.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,I told you not to do that!\NStop playing with the Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:30.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? So how come?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:31.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:33.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, because...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:36.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:41.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:45.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's making a sound,\Nlike it's humming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:46.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:51.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're right!\NIt's humming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:52.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,It sounds like a whistle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:54.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,You too, Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:05.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well? Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:09.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can hear a humming sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:11.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:45.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:48.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,So that day has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:52.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please give us a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:57.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you mind waiting\Nuntil we've finished eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:06.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have negotiations\Nbroken down then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:09.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia is the symbol\Nof Simulacrum Kyuukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:12.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Undoubtedly it is to our\Nsuperiors' advantage that she...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:14.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,...maintain her current silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:18.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, should Onasia\Ndecide to make a move...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:22.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,I certainly don't enjoy conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:23.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:26.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bringing Onasia here\Nat a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.15,0:05:29.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just don't understand what the\Nhigh priestess could be thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Suppose I...
Comment: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:33.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Suppose I...\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:36.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:59.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Taking off in the Simouns\Nwithout authorization...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:01.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is an unprecedented infraction!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where is your sense\Nof responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:05.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:09.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do we recognize that we're Simoun\Nsibyllae and take pride in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:12.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I would say that's true\Nof each and every one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:18.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that all you have to say to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:21.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,If so, please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:31.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,You little brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:46.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vura...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:49.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,And Roatreamon and Alty, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:51.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just as we thought, Paraietta...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:54.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,You couldn't sleep either, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neither could we.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, is the whole gang here then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:41.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,We shall send Onasia\Nback on the Messis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril, Sibylla Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:48.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,May I ask you to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:54.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you not want to know more\Nabout that different world?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:07:58.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:00.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Will you take me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:01.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:04.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, we cannot go in\Nsuch great numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:07.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:29.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:32.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:33.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I'd call it good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:38.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a little bitter, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:41.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,And it's also a little bit sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:45.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,But it's not that\NI don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I can finish it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:51.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I don't know..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:53.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:56.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,You've stopped saying\Nthat all the time, Rimone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:58.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:00.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:03.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that if you really think about it,\Nthere's nothing you can't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:04.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:06.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:11.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,The more I think about\Nsomething, the more lost I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:15.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:22.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, let's finish eating,\Nand then we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:23.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:29.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:35.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,The high priestess\Nhas ordered us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:37.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to make this as smooth\Na flight as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder where we're headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:55.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:56.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:00.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia-sama is at rest now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:01.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:20.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:25.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did she bring up\Nthe "different world"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:27.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,That high priestess...\NThere's something about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:31.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure, the military councilor's\Nan annoying old man too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:33.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but that high priestess...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:39.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:42.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:43.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,...they're so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't treat me like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:52.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,War makes things that\Nshould be obvious...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,...so very hard\Nto see, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:03.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:07.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,There is something\Nyou wish to ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:12.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,You told me that you\Ncould hear Mamina's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:15.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,So... what about my comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:20.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have their souls been released?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:27.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,The one who really\Nwishes to be released...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:29.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is you yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:36.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,By placing yourself at the\Nbrink of your comrades' deaths...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:40.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,...you are actually trying to flee\Nas far as possible from those deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:55.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:56.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,We seem to have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:44.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why the Ruins?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:54.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,There it goes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:56.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,The door to a new world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:13:00.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,The melody played\Nby that music box...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:05.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,...as well as the unintended destination\Nof those who lost their lives here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:06.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:11.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,This was once the training\Nground for Chor Dextra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:13.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Dextra?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:15.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:18.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that was the chor your own\Ngrandfather served as regina for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:21.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Grandpa... a regina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:38.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:39.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,That day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:42.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happened that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:44.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,What day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:46.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,On the Messis...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:50.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,It all came surging back...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:51.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:54.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,The moment I looked into\Nthe helical motors...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was as if I was seeing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:57.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Somebody's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:13:59.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,The memory of something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:05.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,What you see there is\Nnothing but a helix.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:08.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,As it turns out, the only thing\Nwe're capable of understanding is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:12.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:29.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:40.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,And then we became enthralled\Nwith Ri Majons... and the Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:44.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,But that was because we had nothing\Nbut the Simouns to cling to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:46.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:49.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,If the Simouns had never\Nexisted in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:52.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Or even if they had existed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:54.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but no one ever\Ndiscovered how to use them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:55.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,...then what would have happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:14:58.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:00.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:02.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:04.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:19.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,We brought them here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:20.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,We brought them here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:22.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:42.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Long, long ago, there was a\Ncivilization far superior to ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:46.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,And it is said that the Simouns\Nwere in existence at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:51.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,But after a succession\Nof wars broke out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:53.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the country was left in ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:56.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,And once all of the lands\Nwere rendered worthless...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:58.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,...there was no longer\Nany reason to wage war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:02.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,The starving multitudes no\Nlonger needed the Simouns...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:03.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and eventually they\Nforgot how to use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:06.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,The people...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:09.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,...had no choice but to wait for\Ncertain destruction at nature's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:18.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was then that something\Nbroke through the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:20.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and a Simoun arrived\Nfrom a different world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:26.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,On board that Simoun\Nwere two children of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,These young girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:33.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,These young girls announced\Nthemselves as "Simoun sibyllae."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:37.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,They then shared the secret\Nof the Emerald Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:39.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,To a different world...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:46.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, that which transports one to a\Ndifferent time, the ultimate Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:51.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is a divine gift.\NA magnificent "if."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:55.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,What if during that era...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:58.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,...they had told the people\Nthat another war was coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:02.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,If the Simouns hadn't existed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:05.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,...then I might never\Nhave existed either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:07.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,If, during that era...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:10.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,...they found a way to convince the\Npeople of the need for Simouns...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:18.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,But if I'd never existed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:21.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,...then this pain never\Nwould've existed either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:25.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,This era so full of hardship\Nand strife might be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:27.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,To transcend time and space...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:31.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and offer this\N"if" to some other era.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:33.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,That is precisely the purpose...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:36.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,...of the Simouns and\Nof the Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:38.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Transcend time and space?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:40.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable... How could that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:44.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! Then what about this\NChor Dextra you say my grandpa led?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:46.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Dextra...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:50.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,...was created for the sole purpose\Nof completing the Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:54.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Someone you know very well was\Nalso a former member of this chor.
Comment: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:18:01.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,She is the last surviving\Nmember of Chor Dextra.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:07.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:12.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I had the misfortune to find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:22.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,That everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:26.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,That everything that\Nhappened started with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:45.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just now...
Comment: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:46.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:49.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought about what\Nyou just said, Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:52.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know, if the Simouns\Nhad never existed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:55.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they hadn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:57.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:19:00.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then I never would've met\Neveryone in Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:02.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,And, Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:05.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I never would've met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:16.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:17.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:19.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:20.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:22.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:24.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because it hurts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:25.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,What else...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:26.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:30.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:32.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:39.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:43.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean go without\Nknowing where again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:46.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do know where.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:12.23,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Under the blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:17.94,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Beyond the white clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:23.46,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,It's as blue as a tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:28.82,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,As white as a lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:34.65,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,In the pitch-black darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:40.32,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,The light of a red flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:49.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra most likely\Ncompleted the Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:50.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:53.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,She is alive in another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:59.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra and Sibylla\NRimone are both alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:01.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am certain that they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:02.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:05.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:07.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:11.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,...does that mean that Amuria\Nmay also be alive somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:19.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon was a\Ndivine gift. Our only hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:23.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whether it will take us into the\Nfuture or back into the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:25.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,That is not for us to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:27.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:31.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it is by the will of the gods of\NTempus Spatium that the Simouns exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:33.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.63,0:21:35.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the gods cannot be mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:41.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am positive that they will\Nopen the door to the correct era.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:43.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:44.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:47.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I would like to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:48.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,...entrust this task to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.47,0:21:52.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:03.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:07.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,You say it's a Simoun\Nfrom the Arcus Niger?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.69,0:22:09.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Military councilor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.73,0:22:11.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.96,0:22:14.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Arcus Niger...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.49,0:22:16.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,...was shot down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.23,0:22:18.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Seven o'clock! Five ancient\NSimouns approaching fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:23.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:48.00,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.00,0:22:52.24,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.24,0:22:59.31,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.31,0:23:06.90,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:19.79,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I want to get closer to you.\NI want to feel your pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:24.97,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.97,0:23:28.94,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:32.98,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.98,0:23:38.85,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.85,0:23:44.39,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the\Nsky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.39,0:23:47.83,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.83,0:23:53.49,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.49,0:23:59.72,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:06.67,Titles,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.17,0:24:08.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Shoukoku-Plumbum highlands allied forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.50,0:24:10.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,...have begun their\Ninvasion of Kyuukoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.59,0:24:12.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and the attacks are\Nincreasing by the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.93,0:24:15.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.18,0:24:17.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sortie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.51,0:24:20.02,Titles,,0,0,0,,Sortie
